channel.title: In-Game World Switcher implemented!
channel.description:
Implemented just now.
I have to go to bed, but what I have gathered:
[ul][li]On the login screen[/li] [li]Downloads the file http://runescape.com/slr.ws?order=LPWM through a HTTP GET request (a binary file containing ID, population, locale, and server-name?), and parses it using Stream I imagine[/li] [li]Crappy hack rendering of world flags and numbers :D[/li] [li]Possibly uses showDocument(String url) or other method to open the new webpage[/li][/ul]
Check it out, maybe something else cool was implemented.
